    "content": "<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Symmetric Cryptography | Visual Exploration</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary: #6c5ce7;\n            --secondary: #a29bfe;\n            --dark: #2d3436;\n            --light: #f5f6fa;\n            --accent: #00cec9;\n        }\n\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);\n            color: var(--dark);\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--accent));\n            -webkit-background-clip: text;\n            background-clip: text;\n            color: transparent;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .subtitle {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            color: var(--dark);\n            opacity: 0.8;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .visualization {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin: 4rem 0;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .process-flow {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 900px;\n            margin: 2rem 0;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .step {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            width: 30%;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n            transition: all 0.5s ease;\n        }\n\n        .step:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n        }\n\n        .step-icon {\n            width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: white;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .step-icon::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50%;\n            left: -50%;\n            width: 200%;\n            height: 200%;\n            background: conic-gradient(\n                transparent, transparent, transparent, var(--primary)\n            );\n            animation: rotate 4s linear infinite;\n        }\n\n        .step-icon-inner {\n            width: 90px;\n            height: 90px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: white;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n\n        .step-icon svg {\n            width: 40px;\n            height: 40px;\n            color: var(--primary);\n        }\n\n        .step-title {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            color: var(--dark);\n        }\n\n        .step-desc {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            color: var(--dark);\n            opacity: 0.7;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n\n        .arrow {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 40px;\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 10px;\n            background: var(--secondary);\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .arrow::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            right: -10px;\n            top: -5px;\n            width: 0;\n            height: 0;\n            border-left: 10px solid var(--secondary);\n            border-top: 10px solid transparent;\n            border-bottom: 10px solid transparent;\n        }\n\n        .arrow-1 {\n            left: 30%;\n        }\n\n        .arrow-2 {\n            left: 63%;\n        }\n\n        .key-visual {\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            height: 120px;\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            margin: 3rem 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .key-visual::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, \n                transparent 0%, \n                rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.2) 50%, \n                transparent 100%);\n            animation: shimmer 3s infinite;\n        }\n\n        .key-content {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n            width: 90%;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .key-title {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            color: var(--primary);\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        .key-value {\n            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            color: var(--dark);\n            background: rgba(162, 155, 254, 0.1);\n            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        .cipher-demo {\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            margin: 2rem 0;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .cipher-demo::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 5px;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--primary), var(--accent));\n        }\n\n        .cipher-title {\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n            color: var(--dark);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .cipher-title svg {\n            margin-right: 10px;\n            color: var(--primary);\n        }\n\n        .message-box {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .message {\n            width: 48%;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            background: var(--light);\n            position: relative;\n            min-height: 120px;\n        }\n\n        .message-label {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -10px;\n            left: 15px;\n            background: white;\n            padding: 0 10px;\n            font-size: 0.8rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: var(--primary);\n        }\n\n        .message-content {\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .controls {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .btn {\n            padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--accent));\n            color: white;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.4);\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            outline: none;\n            margin: 0 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .btn:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.6);\n        }\n\n        .btn:active {\n            transform: translateY(1px);\n        }\n\n        .btn-secondary {\n            background: white;\n            color: var(--primary);\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary);\n        }\n\n        .algorithm-showcase {\n            margin-top: 4rem;\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .algorithm {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .algorithm:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .algorithm::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 5px;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--accent));\n        }\n\n        .algorithm-title {\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            color: var(--dark);\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        .algorithm-desc {\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            color: var(--dark);\n            opacity: 0.8;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .algorithm-meta {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            font-size: 0.8rem;\n            color: var(--primary);\n            font-weight: 500;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 5rem;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            color: var(--dark);\n            opacity: 0.7;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes rotate {\n            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }\n            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes shimmer {\n            0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }\n            100% { transform: translateX(100%); }\n        }\n\n        .pulse {\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.4); }\n            70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 15px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0); }\n            100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(108, 92, 231, 0); }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <header>\n            <h1>Symmetric Cryptography</h1>\n            <p class=\"subtitle\">A visual exploration of the elegant process where the same secret key is used for both encryption and decryption, ensuring fast and secure communication.</p>\n        </header>\n\n        <div class=\"visualization\">\n            <div class=\"process-flow\">\n                <div class=\"step\">\n                    <div class=\"step-icon\">\n                        <div class=\"step-icon-inner\">\n                            <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                                <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z\" />\n                            </svg>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"step-title\">Key Generation</h3>\n                    <p class=\"step-desc\">A secret key is generated using a cryptographically secure algorithm</p>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"arrow arrow-1\"></div>\n\n                <div class=\"step\">\n                    <div class=\"step-icon\">\n                        <div class=\"step-icon-inner\">\n                            <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                                <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6\" />\n                            </svg>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"step-title\">Encryption</h3>\n                    <p class=\"step-desc\">Plaintext is transformed into ciphertext using the secret key</p>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"arrow arrow-2\"></div>\n\n                <div class=\"step\">\n                    <div class=\"step-icon\">\n                        <div class=\"step-icon-inner\">\n                            <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                                <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M3 10h10a8 8 0 018 8v2M3 10l6 6m-6-6l6-6\" />\n                            </svg>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"step-title\">Decryption</h3>\n                    <p class=\"step-desc\">Ciphertext is transformed back to plaintext using the same key</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"key-visual pulse\">\n                <div class=\"key-content\">\n                    <div class=\"key-title\">Secret Key</div>\n                    <div class=\"key-value\">AES-256: 7f4a8d3c1b6e5f2a9d0c3b7e8f1a2d5</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"cipher-demo\">\n                <h2 class=\"cipher-title\">\n                    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n                        <rect x=\"2\" y=\"6\" width=\"20\" height=\"12\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect>\n                        <path d=\"M12 12h.01\"></path>\n                        <path d=\"M17 12h.01\"></path>\n                        <path d=\"M7 12h.01\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                    Encryption/Decryption Demo\n                </h2>\n\n                <div class=\"message-box\">\n                    <div class=\"message\">\n                        <div class=\"message-label\">Plaintext</div>\n                        <div class=\"message-content\" id=\"plaintext\">The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"message\">\n                        <div class=\"message-label\">Ciphertext</div>\n                        <div class=\"message-content\" id=\"ciphertext\">U2FsdGVkX1+3qJ5J5v7fKz4j9LkZwQ1tXJ6eY8vHjLw=</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"controls\">\n                    <button class=\"btn\" id=\"encryptBtn\">Encrypt</button>\n                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" id=\"decryptBtn\">Decrypt</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"algorithm-showcase\">\n            <div class=\"algorithm\">\n                <h3 class=\"algorithm-title\">AES (Advanced Encryption Standard)</h3>\n                <p class=\"algorithm-desc\">The gold standard in symmetric encryption, using 128, 192 or 256-bit keys. Adopted by the U.S. government and used worldwide.</p>\n                <div class=\"algorithm-meta\">\n                    <span>Block Cipher</span>\n                    <span>Key sizes: 128/192/256-bit</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"algorithm\">\n                <h3 class=\"algorithm-title\">ChaCha20</h3>\n                <p class=\"algorithm-desc\">A modern stream cipher designed for high performance in software implementations, often used as an alternative to AES.</p>\n                <div class=\"algorithm-meta\">\n                    <span>Stream Cipher</span>\n                    <span>Key size: 256-bit</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"algorithm\">\n                <h3 class=\"algorithm-title\">Twofish</h3>\n                <p class=\"algorithm-desc\">A symmetric key block cipher with a block size of 128 bits and key sizes up to 256 bits, known for its flexibility.</p>\n                <div class=\"algorithm-meta\">\n                    <span>Block Cipher</span>\n                    <span>Key sizes: 128/192/256-bit</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <footer>\n            <p>© 2023 Symmetric Cryptography Visual Exploration | Designed with elegance</p>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n            const encryptBtn = document.getElementById('encryptBtn');\n            const decryptBtn = document.getElementById('decryptBtn');\n            const plaintext = document.getElementById('plaintext');\n            const ciphertext = document.getElementById('ciphertext');\n\n            encryptBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {\n                ciphertext.textContent = \"U2FsdGVkX1+3qJ5J5v7fKz4j9LkZwQ1tXJ6eY8vHjLw=\";\n                ciphertext.style.animation = 'none';\n                ciphertext.offsetHeight; // Trigger reflow\n                ciphertext.style.animation = 'fadeIn 0.5s ease-out';\n            });\n\n            decryptBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {\n                ciphertext.textContent = \"The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog\";\n                ciphertext.style.animation = 'none';\n                ciphertext.offsetHeight; // Trigger reflow\n                ciphertext.style.animation = 'fadeIn 0.5s ease-out';\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"
